dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents zoning for Jefferson County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Jefferson_Zoning_2017.gdb.[This file contains the polygons for all parcels in Jefferson County and the data related to the zone of the parcel.]
uw_supplemental_s: This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2018. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2017. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2018. This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
